snippet.title: Costume CO
snippet.description:
🔴 Join me as I analyze television and film from a costume perspective. With 15 years experience working in theatre,  television and live production, I'll present you with a well researched and thorough analysis of all things costume. And mispronouncing Game of Thrones names at every turn!

👕 Four Weddings and Funeral merch available exclusively at my Costume CO Tee-shirt shop: https://teespring.com/stores/costume-co-merch-4

Some of the links below are affiliate links. I will make a small commission at no additional cost to you if you click through and make a purchase. 

Available on Amazon for pre-order: Game of Thrones: The Costumes (Hardcover) by Michele Clapton, November 5, 2019. Pre-order Price Guarantee:  https://amzn.to/2Cqs4Xh 

Shop Costumes at my Costume CO Amazon Shop: https://www.amazon.com/shop/costumeco

May 24, 2019 15,748 Subs
